						<summary>

						<p>Another Slab kept in the Chennakēśava temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1604, Dundubhi, Chaitra śu. 10</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1682 A.D. April 10, Friday.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record a gift of land to the god Śri Mallikhārjuna at Pedayakalūru. Other details are lost.</p>						

						</summary>
